1.Unzip the files
2.Install node modules by npm install
3.Run the MongoDb connection
4.Then run the Server by node index.js command
5.Check for api CRUD
6.Check for erros in Postman

API made:-


POST Register --> http://localhost:8080/api/register

{
      "name":"Rahul",
      "email":"rahul@gmail.com",
       "password":"password"
    }
POST Login  -->http://localhost:8080/api/login

{
        "email":"rahul@gmail.com",
        "password":"password"
    }
    
 POST Add Todo --> http://localhost:8080/api/todo

{
        "title": "Reading",
        "shortDescription": "must do fhfg hfgh thfgh hfgh tutut tutjt tut ",
        "longDescription": "rytrtrt ytfy rtutut tutu tutu tutu trutu tuutu tut tutu tutu",
        "author": "Rahul"
        
GET Todos --> http://localhost:8080/api/todos

{
        "title": "Rahul kjMust do",
        "shortDescription": "must do fhfg hfgh thfgh hfgh tutut tutjt tut ",
        "longDescription": "rytrtrt ytfy rtutut tutu tutu tutu trutu tuutu tut tutu tutu",
        "author": "rtert"
        
GET Todo --> http://localhost:8080/api/todo/:id

{
       "title": "Read Book Titin",
        "shortDescription": "A book of adventure thrill & readable purposes ",
